textBeforeTable: South Brunswick Vikings 35, Hillsborough Raiders 21 Here is South Brunswick's awesome box provided by Daniel Solomon each week: South Brunswick beat Hillsborough in last year's playoffs, 63-14. South Brunswick is 3-1 lifetime vs. Hillsborough, including three in a row by a combined score of 112-35. Hillsborough was making its 13th appearance and is 8-11 with two titles. South Brunswick is making its fifth playoff appearance and fourth in six years. The Vikings are 3-4 in the playoffs and seeking their first crown. South Brunswick is averaging 30.1 points per game. South Brunswick is 24-6 in its last 30 games. NOTES: All told, Perkowski has passed for 1,020 yards and 9 TD's, while rushing for 612 yards and 10 TD's. That's a total of 1,632 yards and 19 touchdowns. He has passed for over 100 yards in five games, while rushing for 100 in four games. either running or passing. T.J.
